{"chunk_id": "clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook_001", "source_name": "清算金额不平复核手册（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/amount-mismatch", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "清算金额与核心入账金额不一致", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "clearing_operations", "audit_trail"], "content": "清算文件金额与核心入账金额不一致时，应先核对交易参考号、渠道流水号、币种、手续费字段和入账净额口径，避免把手续费净额差异误判为本金差错。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`BC-R002` 命中后必须输出清算金额、核心金额、差额和疑似口径，不得只给出“金额不平”的泛化结论。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook_002", "source_name": "清算金额不平复核手册（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/amount-mismatch", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "手续费净额差异核查", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "clearing_operations", "audit_trail"], "content": "部分渠道以清算净额入账，核心侧可能记录交易本金与手续费分录。复核时应同时查看手续费科目、商户费率和清算批次汇总。\n\n本项目抽象规则：若差额等于手续费或服务费，应提示按净额口径复核，并保留费率、手续费分录和批次号作为证据。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook_003", "source_name": "清算金额不平复核手册（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/amount-mismatch", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "退款冲正造成的金额偏差", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "clearing_operations", "audit_trail"], "content": "同一业务参考号存在退款、撤销或冲正时，清算侧可能出现负向流水或汇总抵扣。金额复核应把正向交易与冲正流水合并判断。\n\n本项目抽象规则：同参考号存在反向金额时，AuditAgent 应提示核对冲正链路，不能直接输出单笔短款或长款结论。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook_004", "source_name": "清算金额不平复核手册（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/amount-mismatch", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "汇总批次与单笔金额穿透", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "clearing_operations", "audit_trail"], "content": "当清算文件只提供批次汇总金额时，应穿透到批次明细或渠道对账单，确认差额来自单笔漏入、重复入账还是批次口径不一致。\n\n本项目抽象规则：没有单笔明细证据时必须转人工复核，并在 evidence 中说明缺少批次明细。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_cutoff_t1_guideline_001", "source_name": "支付清算跨日切 T+1 补记处理指引（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/cutoff-t1", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_cutoff_t1_guideline.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "日切窗口内的清算单边处理", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["cutoff_cross_day", "t1_trace", "audit_trail"], "content": "清算侧在日切窗口内出现单边流水时，不能直接按普通单边差错结论处理，应先判断是否存在核心侧 T+1 补记的可能，并保留跨日切证据。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`BC-R003` 命中后应优先提示“T+1 已配对”或“待 T+1 补齐”，并记录清算交易时间、清算日期、候选核心流水号和记账日期。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_cutoff_t1_guideline_002", "source_name": "支付清算跨日切 T+1 补记处理指引（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/cutoff-t1", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_cutoff_t1_guideline.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "T+1 补记核查要素", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["cutoff_cross_day", "t1_trace", "audit_trail"], "content": "跨日切追溯至少核查金额、参考号或商户订单号、以及核心侧记账日期是否为清算交易日期次日。缺少任一关键要素时，不能自动确认补记完成。\n\n本项目抽象规则：TraceAgent 和 AuditAgent 只能基于命中的候选要素输出补记建议，候选为空时必须保留人工补查动作。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_file_exception_playbook_001", "source_name": "清算文件异常处理指引（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/file-exception", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_file_exception_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "清算文件缺失", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["clearing_file_exception", "file_integrity", "audit_trail"], "content": "清算文件未到达时，应先核对文件传输状态、渠道通知、批次日期和重传窗口。不得用上一批次文件代替本批次清算依据。\n\n本项目抽象规则：文件缺失只能输出待补文件或人工追踪动作，不能生成自动平账建议。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_file_exception_playbook_002", "source_name": "清算文件异常处理指引（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/file-exception", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_file_exception_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "文件重复导入", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["clearing_file_exception", "file_integrity", "audit_trail"], "content": "同一清算批次文件重复导入会造成核心侧或清算侧虚增流水。复核时应比较文件名、批次号、渠道机构号、记录总数和总金额。\n\n本项目抽象规则：重复导入证据闭环时应提示撤销重复批次或隔离重复数据，并记录重复文件标识。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_file_exception_playbook_003", "source_name": "清算文件异常处理指引（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/file-exception", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_file_exception_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "文件格式或字段缺损", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["clearing_file_exception", "file_integrity", "audit_trail"], "content": "文件格式异常、关键字段为空或编码错误时，应先拒绝自动对账，保留原始文件、解析错误和缺失字段清单。\n\n本项目抽象规则：缺少交易参考号、金额或交易时间时，TraceAgent 不得构造候选匹配。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_file_exception_playbook_004", "source_name": "清算文件异常处理指引（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/file-exception", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_file_exception_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "文件日期与清算日期不一致", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["clearing_file_exception", "file_integrity", "audit_trail"], "content": "文件名日期、文件内清算日期和业务交易日期不一致时，应以渠道清算规则确认归属批次，并检查是否为跨日切或补发文件。\n\n本项目抽象规则：日期口径冲突时应输出需人工确认的日期字段，不得默认采用系统导入日期。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_query_reply_playbook_001", "source_name": "清算查询查复作业说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/query-reply", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_query_reply_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "查询发起条件", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["query_reply", "single_side_missing", "audit_trail"], "content": "清算单边、金额不平、参考号不一致或文件缺失经本地证据无法闭环时，应向渠道或清算机构发起查询查复。\n\n本项目抽象规则：RAG 命中查询查复时，next_action 应指向人工发起查复或等待回执，不得自动确认差错归因。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_query_reply_playbook_002", "source_name": "清算查询查复作业说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/query-reply", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_query_reply_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "查复所需字段", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["query_reply", "single_side_missing", "audit_trail"], "content": "查询查复至少包含渠道机构号、清算日期、交易参考号、金额、交易时间、商户订单号和现有侧流水号。\n\n本项目抽象规则：缺少任一查复字段时，AuditAgent 应说明缺失字段，避免输出无法执行的查复建议。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_query_reply_playbook_003", "source_name": "清算查询查复作业说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/query-reply", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_query_reply_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "查复回执归档", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["query_reply", "single_side_missing", "audit_trail"], "content": "查复回执应关联原始异常、任务号和处置结论。回执确认对方已清算但本方未入账时，应进入核心补账或人工复核流程。\n\n本项目抽象规则：回执内容必须作为 evidence 记录来源，不允许把未收到回执的状态写成已确认。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_query_reply_playbook_004", "source_name": "清算查询查复作业说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/query-reply", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_query_reply_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "超时未复处理", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["query_reply", "single_side_missing", "audit_trail"], "content": "超过约定时限仍未收到查复回执时，应升级人工跟进，并保留发起时间、催办记录和当前风险说明。\n\n本项目抽象规则：查复超时不改变原异常类型，只改变 next_action 和风险提示。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_reconciliation_scope_001", "source_name": "支付结算对账口径说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/reconciliation-scope", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_reconciliation_scope.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "清算对账字段口径", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "clearing_file_exception", "audit_trail"], "content": "清算对账需要同时核验清算流水、核心入账流水、金额字段和业务参考号。出现文件缺失、金额不平或跨日补记时，应根据清算业务口径区分异常类型，不得沿用银企场景的客户侧解释。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`BANK_CLEARING` 场景的 RAG 依据必须来自清算领域资料，避免把银企查询查复话术误用到清算跨日切异常。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_reconciliation_scope_002", "source_name": "支付结算对账口径说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/reconciliation-scope", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_reconciliation_scope.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "自动结论边界", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "clearing_file_exception", "audit_trail"], "content": "只有在金额、业务单号和记账日期证据闭环时，系统才能输出已配对或可自动平账建议。证据不完整时必须转人工，并在原因中说明缺失项。\n\n本项目抽象规则：清算 RAG 无命中、或命中但不能支撑结论时，工作流仍需保持人工兜底，不允许编造规则来源。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_reference_match_playbook_001", "source_name": "清算参考号匹配规则说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/reference-match", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_reference_match_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "参考号一致优先", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["reference_match", "t1_trace", "clearing_operations"], "content": "清算流水与核心流水匹配时，优先使用交易参考号、商户订单号或渠道流水号。金额相同但参考号不一致时不能直接配对。\n\n本项目抽象规则：TraceAgent 候选匹配必须展示使用的参考字段，不能只依据金额和日期。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_reference_match_playbook_002", "source_name": "清算参考号匹配规则说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/reference-match", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_reference_match_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "参考号截断或补零", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["reference_match", "t1_trace", "clearing_operations"], "content": "部分渠道会对参考号做截断、补零或前缀转换。复核时应记录转换规则，并保留原始字段与规范化字段。\n\n本项目抽象规则：仅在转换规则可解释时才允许输出候选匹配；规则缺失时转人工。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_reference_match_playbook_003", "source_name": "清算参考号匹配规则说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/reference-match", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_reference_match_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "一对多与多对一匹配", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["reference_match", "t1_trace", "clearing_operations"], "content": "清算汇总或拆分入账会形成一对多、多对一关系。复核时应比较汇总金额、明细数量和业务关联号。\n\n本项目抽象规则：拆分或汇总匹配需要列出全部候选明细，证据不足时不能自动平账。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_reference_match_playbook_004", "source_name": "清算参考号匹配规则说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/reference-match", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_reference_match_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "弱匹配风险", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["reference_match", "t1_trace", "clearing_operations"], "content": "只有金额和日期相近、缺少参考号证据的匹配属于弱匹配，应保留风险标记并进入人工复核。\n\n本项目抽象规则：弱匹配不得提升 confidence 到高置信区间，next_action 应保持人工确认。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_single_side_playbook_001", "source_name": "清算单边差错处置手册（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/single-side", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_single_side_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "非日切窗口单边核查", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["single_side_missing", "query_reply", "clearing_operations"], "content": "清算侧或核心侧只有一边存在流水，且不在日切窗口内时，应按普通清算单边差错处理，进入查询查复或人工复核流程，不得直接平账。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`BC-R001` 需要输出缺失侧、现有侧金额、来源文件和建议动作，默认指向人工或查询查复。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_single_side_playbook_002", "source_name": "清算单边差错处置手册（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/single-side", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_single_side_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "证据留存要求", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["single_side_missing", "query_reply", "clearing_operations"], "content": "单边差错的复核记录应保留来源系统、交易流水号、参考号、金额、交易时间和处置结论，保证后续可以追溯。\n\n本项目抽象规则：无论是否命中 RAG，单边差错都需要把规则依据和证据链一起写入审计结果或人工复核说明。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_t1_supplement_playbook_001", "source_name": "清算 T+1 补账追踪说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/t1-supplement", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_t1_supplement_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "日切前后交易归属", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["cutoff_cross_day", "t1_trace", "single_side_missing"], "content": "接近日切时间的交易应同时核对交易发生时间、渠道清算日期和核心记账日期。跨日归属不能只按自然日判断。\n\n本项目抽象规则：日切边界命中时，必须输出参与判断的三个日期时间字段。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_t1_supplement_playbook_002", "source_name": "清算 T+1 补账追踪说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/t1-supplement", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_t1_supplement_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "T+1 已补记判断", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["cutoff_cross_day", "t1_trace", "single_side_missing"], "content": "若核心侧次日存在同金额、同参考号或可解释参考号转换的流水，可提示 T+1 已补记，但仍需记录补记流水号。\n\n本项目抽象规则：T+1 已补记结论必须包含候选核心流水号和记账日期。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_t1_supplement_playbook_003", "source_name": "清算 T+1 补账追踪说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/t1-supplement", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_t1_supplement_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "T+1 待补齐判断", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["cutoff_cross_day", "t1_trace", "single_side_missing"], "content": "清算侧已有交易但核心侧次日仍未出现候选流水时，应标记为待补齐或人工跟进，不得自动平账。\n\n本项目抽象规则：候选为空时 next_action 指向人工补查，evidence 不得伪造核心流水。"}
{"chunk_id": "clearing_t1_supplement_playbook_004", "source_name": "清算 T+1 补账追踪说明（模拟摘录）", "source_url": "https://example.com/bank-clearing/t1-supplement", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_clearing/clearing_t1_supplement_playbook.md", "source_type": "markdown", "section_title": "补账失败回退", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["cutoff_cross_day", "t1_trace", "single_side_missing"], "content": "如果补账任务失败或被冲销，应回退为清算单边异常，并重新进入查询查复或人工复核。\n\n本项目抽象规则：补账失败不能继续沿用已配对状态，应保留失败原因和回退动作。"}
